            "Icon": "skillicon/icon_skill_mifu_01",
            "IconConditions": {},
            "Element": "Physical",
            "Name": "Qingbo Triplex",
            "Desc": "Keep casting Mi Fu's battle skill to unleash 3 different moves. The first battle skill cast is <@ba.key>Cloudtrapper</>.\n<@ba.key>MOVE 1 - Cloudtrapper</>: Costs <@ba.vup>100</> SP and <#ba.return>returns</><@ba.vup> 50</> SP after casting; Mi Fu fires a grappling chain from her gauntlets that deals <@ba.pd>Physical DMG</> to the target and nearby enemies, then attempts to pull the target and nearby enemies towards her. After casting MOVE 1, the next battle skill will be temporarily replaced with <@ba.key>Trail and Mangle</>.\n<@ba.key>MOVE 2 - Trail and Mangle</>: Costs <@ba.vup>50</> SP; Mi Fu unleashes a flurry of punches that deals <@ba.pd>Physical DMG</> with the final punch applying <#ba.crush>Crush</>. If this Crush <#ba.consume>consumes</> at least 3 <#ba.noguard>Vulnerability</> stacks from a single target, then the next battle skill will be temporarily replaced with <@ba.key>World Splitter</>.\n<@ba.key>MOVE 3 - World Splitter</>: Costs <@ba.vup>50</> SP; Mi Fu deals massive <@ba.pd>Physical DMG</> to a specified area; this DMG is not treated as Battle Skill DMG, but as <#ba.crush>Crush</> DMG.",
